{"tid":1205385,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果警方對我作出不當行為（例如非法闖入私人地方或以武力迫供），我可以怎樣投訴他們？","createTime":"2019-06-11T18:29:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T18:29:49.000Z","uid":171074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3386ed79ceceb16e5e7d9cc9855a28f2c894fc7a","tid":1205385,"uid":171074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T18:29:49.000Z","msg":"14. 如果警方對我作出不當行為（例如非法闖入私人地方或以武力迫供），我可以怎樣投訴他們？<br />\n閣下可<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">親自前往</span></strong>或致函於任何警署內的投訴警察課，或往投訴警察報案中心，地址是：香港灣仔軍器廠街三號堅偉樓附翼地下。[1]<br />\n<br />\n萬一大家受到警方不當行為對待, 可以<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">親自前往</span></strong>任何警署內的投訴警察課(地址：香港灣仔軍器廠街三號堅偉樓附翼地下)作出投訴. 行幾步唔太麻煩.<br />\n<br />\n另外空餘時間多讀警務條例, 對今後集會都有幫助. 詳見條例232章及245章. [2]<br />\n<br />\nRef: <br />\n[1] <a href=\"http://www.clic.org.hk/tc/topics/policeAndCrime/police_powers/q14.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.clic.org.hk%2Ftc%2Ftopics%2FpoliceAndCrime%2Fpolice_powers%2Fq14.shtml&d=NC%2FTzFAtl3V7yegmN9swvpFIS2qdHEMyYfCy%2BeARyBE%3D&h=6f57d101\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.clic.org.hk/tc/topics/policeAndCrime/police_powers/q14.shtml</a><br />\n[2] <a href=\"http://www.hklii.hk/chi/hk/legis/ord/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hklii.hk%2Fchi%2Fhk%2Flegis%2Ford%2F&d=NC%2FTzFAtl3V7yegmN9swvpFIS2qdHEMyYfCy%2BeARyBE%3D&h=dc97f555\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hklii.hk/chi/hk/legis/ord/</a>"}]}